Data Asset Management -aka Data Governance or Data Lineage
For enterprise level data science use Apache Atlas, ODPI Egeria, Kylo
Apache Spark
A key property is that it provides linear scalability which means the more the number of servers in a cluster the more the performance. Apache Flink came afterwards to process real-time data streams and can process images in a stream as well. 
