Libraries APIs
REST API - Representational State Transfer Application Programming Interfaces
Allow you to communicate through the internet. Enable you to use resources like storage, data, and artificially intelligent algorithms. 
APIs allow communication between two pieces of software. 
Machine Learning uses algorithms to identify patterns in the data. The process by which the model learns data patterns is called model training. 
Deep Learning refers to a general set of models and techniques that loosely emulate the way the human brain solves a wide range of problems. 

